        <p><font face="arial,helvetica" size="-1" color="#5b6e96">
        <b>CONVENIENT LOCATION</b></font><br>
        <font face="arial,helvetica" size="-1">
        The Sennin Foundation Center for Japanese Cultural Arts is located
        in Albany, right between Berkeley and El Cerrito. Our dojo can easily
        be found at 1053 San Pablo Avenue, in a safe, well-lit neighborhood
        only 1 1/2 miles from both the El Cerrito Plaza and North Berkeley
        <a href="http://www.bart.gov/">BART</a> stations. <a
        href="http://www.actransit.org/">AC Transit</a>'s 72 bus stops right
        in front of our dojo. To see a map of our location,
        <a href="http://www.mapquest.com/maps/map.adp?country=US&countryid=250&addtohistory=&address=1053+San+Pablo+Avenue&city=Albany&state=CA&zipcode=&submit=Get+Map">
